name: WebStarts
tag_list: free-website, website-builder, make-website, buid-website, create-website, stie-builder
overview:
WebStarts is everything you need to build and maintain your very own free website. This includes your web address, hosting, and website design tools.

http://WebStarts.com has a unique drag and drop interface that allows you to place text, images, videos, and just about anything else exactly where you want it to appear.

http://WebStarts.com let’s you choose a new domain (YourOwn.com) or use an existing domain you registred previously with another company. Upgrade to a WebStarts Pro Account and your domain is automatically configured with your website.

http://WebStarts.com is search engine friendly. That means the type of web pages created with WebStarts are the kind search engines like. Upgrade to a WebStarts Pro Account and your website is automatically submitted to Google, Yahoo, and MSN.

WebStarts includes over 100 features. In additon the WebStarts help documentation includes over 130 training videos that show you how to do everything from add a photo to your site to getting better search engine ranking.
